00:31:56.460 --> 00:32:02.049
to live in luxury for a few days. Before this,
the Kims were depicted very positively. Yes,

391
00:32:02.049 --> 00:32:07.119
they caused mischief to get a little bit ahead,
but you SAW where they came from, with some

392
00:32:07.119 --> 00:32:11.249
comedically heavy-handed metaphors to boot.
